                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When a grindylow successfully Grabs a creature larger than themself, they attach to that creature. The @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Grabbed] creature is not @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Immobilized], but if it moves, the grindylow moves with it.</p>\n<p>If the creature is Medium or smaller, it takes a –5-foot status penalty to its Speeds while the grindylow is attached. The grindylow is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] while attached to a creature.</p>"
                },
